    <item>
      <title>Longer Post</title>
      <link>http://www.fergusfettes.com/posts/longer-post/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Dec 2020 16:45:38 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://www.fergusfettes.com/posts/longer-post/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello world! I&amp;rsquo;m continuing my slightly anachronistic (or preposterous) tour of Web publishing. I started with a threejs megaproject, and now I&amp;rsquo;ve travelled all the way back (via simple paperjs attempts) to a static http website. Marvellous.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I think I&amp;rsquo;ll stay here for a while, build up some foundations, then head back up the ladder of complexity. Maybe one day I will finish my 3d playground!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This microblog is written on my phone in gitjournal, built with Hugo (I still don&amp;rsquo;t have a build pipeline set up so I run the following script whenever I want to update the site), then published with GitHub pages. Marvellous!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;#!/usr/bin/env bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
cd journal
git pull
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
cd ffettes
rm -rf public/*
hugo -D
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
cd ffettes/public
git add .
git commit -am &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$1&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
git push
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

git add .
git commit -am &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$1&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
